    "Defining Adherence: Making Sense of Physical Activity Tracker Data.txt",
    "Exploring the Design Space of Glanceable Feedback for Physical Activity Trackers.txt",
    "Fine-grained Sharing of Sensed Physical Activity: A Value Sensitive Approach.txt",
